  <entry>
    <title>文章置顶和隐藏的技巧</title>
    <link href="/2024/03/17/%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E7%BD%AE%E9%A1%B6%E5%92%8C%E9%9A%90%E8%97%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/"/>
    <url>/2024/03/17/%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E7%BD%AE%E9%A1%B6%E5%92%8C%E9%9A%90%E8%97%8F%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="文章排序"><a href="#文章排序" class="headerlink" title="文章排序"></a>文章排序</h2><p>在文章开头 front-matter (opens new window)中配置 sticky 属性：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ ---<br>  title: 文章标题<br>  index_img: /img/example.jpg<br>  <span class="hljs-built_in">date</span>: 2019-10-10 10:00:00<br>  sticky: 100<br>  ---<br>  以下是文章内容<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>sticky越大,文章越靠前</p><h3 id="关闭和修改前置图标"><a href="#关闭和修改前置图标" class="headerlink" title="关闭和修改前置图标"></a>关闭和修改前置图标</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ index:<br>   post_sticky:<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">enable</span>: <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    icon: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;iconfont icon-top&#x27;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>前往主题配置修改</p><h2 id="隐藏文章"><a href="#隐藏文章" class="headerlink" title="隐藏文章"></a>隐藏文章</h2><p>把某些文章隐藏，不在首页和其他归档分类页里展示，可以在文章开头 front-matter (opens new window)中配置 hide: true 属性。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ <br>---<br>title: 文章标题<br>index_img: /img/example.jpg<br><span class="hljs-built_in">date</span>: 2019-10-10 10:00:00<br>hide: <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>---<br>以下是文章内容<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="归档文章"><a href="#归档文章" class="headerlink" title="归档文章"></a>归档文章</h2><p>只是想让文章在首页隐藏，但仍需要在归档分类页里展示，可以在文章开头 front-matter (opens new window)中配置 archive: true 属性</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$<br>---<br>title: 文章标题<br>index_img: /img/example.jpg<br><span class="hljs-built_in">date</span>: 2019-10-10 10:00:00<br>archive: <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>---<br>以下是文章内容<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
